Contact customer support for South Carolina Electric & Gas if you need help accessing your account or resetting your password. Visit their support page here: www.sceg.com.


Can I access my account or pay South Carolina Electric & Gas from my phone or tablet?
Unfortunately South Carolina Electric & Gas does not offer a mobile app.  You can use the doxo My Account Manager app to keep your account info, notes, documents, and contact information for South Carolina Electric & Gas.  Download and install doxo My Account Manager for iPhone or doxo My Account Manager for Android now.


How do I contact South Carolina Electric & Gas if I have a question about my account or bill?
South Carolina Electric & Gas offers customer support via their website at www.sceg.com. You can also contact South Carolina Electric & Gas via phone at 800-251-7234.


Does South Carolina Electric & Gas go by another name?
South Carolina Electric & Gas is also known as: South Carolina Electric & Gas.


 




